<item>
            <title>[TIKA-460] HTMLHandler misses treatment of A elements </title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/TIKA-460</link>
                <project id="12310631" key="TIKA">Tika</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;The A elements should be processed before any other safe element, otherwise it never happens&lt;/p&gt;</description>
